[Action Executor] → emit('supernova:state-change', executing)
         ↓
[Borde: Cyan] → Usuario observa
         ↓
[Safety Layer] → detecta acción crítica → emit('awaiting_confirmation')
         ↓
[Borde: Rojo + Pulse] → UI nativa pide confirmación
         ↓
[Usuario] → Acepta → SafetyEvents.confirmationGranted()
         ↓
[Borde: Cyan] → Reanuda ejecución
         ↓
[Final] → emit('completed') → [Borde: Verde 1.5s] → [Oculta]
